It is fixed in stable/12 but probably worth to merge to releng/12.

run script:

root@clinch1:~ # uname -a
FreeBSD clinch1.musec.engr.mun.ca 12.0-RC1 FreeBSD 12.0-RC1 r340470 GENERIC  amd64
